<keyLead id="BB38A5748E84FF0A48A756D2FA39FDC0" pageId="202" pageNumber="203">1. Protarsal segment 4 less than 0.5 times as long as segment 1; posterior surface of propodeum with two complete longitudinal keels; face only with frontal line, without further longitudinal keels................................. D. sinicus Olmi</keyLead>
