<keyLead id="BB38A5748E84FF0A48A75558FA39FD56" pageId="202" pageNumber="203">2. Disc of pronotum surrounded by one carina forming evident margin (Plate 56B); head and mesosoma mostly testaceous-red-dish................................................................................D. constrictus (Olmi)</keyLead>
